jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.sc

Class SystemObjectType

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.Element
      • jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.sc.SystemObjectType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Element>, OvalObject

    public class SystemObjectType
extends Element
    A reference between items collected and a related global OVAL Object. The name "object" in the OVAL Schema is renamed because the name has the special meaning in Java.
